:name:
Vampiric etiquette

:pool: 
Instinct

:p: 
I

:coretxt:
This ability is used to navigate through complicated social situation that occur when interacting with vampires.
It can be simultaneusly courtesy and politics.
During social situation with vampires, this can be used to survive, or put someone else into difficult position.
As vampires can have a temper, having someone get angry and commit faux pas can have huge consequences.

